---
title: Shawarma-Spiced Braised Chickpeas & Kale with Sweet Potato, Harissa Aioli & Golden Raisins
description: This hearty vegetarian dish is packed with shawarma-spiced chickpeas, earthy kale, and tender sweet potatoes for a wholesome meal that’s sure to satisfy. After braising the veggies, you’ll serve this saucy stew over a bed of fragrant basmati rice. The final touch? A drizzle of harissa aioli for richness and heat, plus a sprinkle of sliced almonds.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67c57312f4b525c8eb5daddf-e54b1ff3.jpeg
